# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# CERTIFY-BTC .gitignore
# Golden rule: NEVER commit data or model weights. They are huge, often
# license-restricted (patient MRIs!), and blow past GitHub's file limits.
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Datasets (place your MRIs here locally; keep them off GitHub) ---
data/
*.nii
*.nii.gz
*.dcm

# --- Model weights / checkpoints ---
checkpoints/
*.pth
*.pt
*.ckpt
*.onnx

# --- Training artifacts ---
logs/
runs/
wandb/
*.log

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# --- Virtual environments ---
venv/
.venv/
env/
ENV/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Notebook output can be huge; keep the checkpoints folder shape only ---
# (We keep an empty checkpoints/ via .gitkeep but ignore its contents above.)
!checkpoints/.gitkeep
!data/.gitkeep
